    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a solid daily driver. Mechanically, it remains in good working order with a steady engine and dependable transmission, though it lacks the refinement of a newer model. The exterior shows its age with various scuffs, small dings, and some fading in the clear coat, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and some minor staining on the carpets. It has been maintained enough to stay on the road safely, but a new owner should expect to address some cosmetic issues and routine maintenance soon. It\u2019s a practical choice for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
