    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Silver Grey Metallic, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to deliver a sharp, linear power band. Performance is further enhanced by a factory-equipped M-Variable limited-slip differential and a rigid chassis. This example has been maintained with technical foresight: the rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system has been bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates\u2014addressing the three critical areas of this platform. While the exterior and interior show minor signs of use consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical vitals are robust, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a crisp shift action. It represents a mechanically sound, driver-focused specimen of BMW's analog era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
