      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though minor road chips consistent with careful use are visible upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is supple with minimal bolstering wear, and all electronic components\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, including a recent comprehensive inspection, oil change, and brake service. The engine delivers smooth, reliable power, and the transmission shifts are crisp and certain. Equipped with a fresh set of all-season tires and a complete service history, this car offers a dependable, high-quality driving experience for the discerning buyer. Includes both original key fobs.",
